trans-unit.source: Specifies where a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"></xref> object is placed in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvor et <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"> </xref> objektet er plassert i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TableRowSection enumeration specifies whether a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> object is placed in the body, header, or footer of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen TableRowSection angir om en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>objektet er plassert i meldingsteksten, toppteksten eller bunnteksten i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>

trans-unit.source: The TableRowSection enumeration represents the possible values for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.TableSection%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> class.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen TableRowSection representerer mulige verdier for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.TableSection%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.TableSection%2A>

trans-unit.source: The TableRowSection enumeration enables you to build accessible Web sites using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control by adding the `thead`, `tbody`, and `tfoot` elements to the HTML that is rendered to the client.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen TableRowSection gjør mulig å bygge tilgjengelig webområder ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontrollen ved å legge til den `thead`, `tbody`, og `tfoot` elementer til HTML gjengis til klienten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>

trans-unit.source: If all rows in a table are in the `tbody` element, the section information is not rendered.
trans-unit.target: Hvis alle radene i en tabell i det `tbody` elementet delen informasjonen er ikke gjengis.

trans-unit.source: At least one row must be in a non-body element.
trans-unit.target: Minst én rad må være et ikke-body-element.

trans-unit.source: When using the declarative syntax, the sections must be in the following order: header, body, and then footer.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker syntaksen deklarerende, delene må være i følgende rekkefølge: topptekst, body og bunntekst.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"></xref> is placed in the body of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"> </xref> er plassert i brødteksten i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"></xref> is placed in the footer of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"> </xref> er plassert i bunnteksten i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"></xref> is placed in the header of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"> </xref> er plassert i filhodet for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref>.
